/><strong>How long does the charge last:<\/strong>15-50 hours depending on usage frequency<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_XdcgxH":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is it suitable as a reading light?","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"row_content":"<p>Yes, it is! Many customers have reviewed our lamp and loved it for reading or as a night light for work.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_NtqQXx":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is there a timer installed in the lamp?","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"row_content":"<p>There is no timer installed. The light turns off when it runs out of battery or when you turn it off.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_tq4B9M":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Can we replace the bulb when it stops working?","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"row_content":"<p>Yes, it is! All our bulbs are efficiently manufactured to last for 2500 hours, after which they need to be replaced.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_gdGJHz":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Does it need to be charged in at all times or is it wireless?","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"row_content":"<p>It can be used completely wirelessly after it has been charged. It can also be used while charged<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_dMYAzm":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is the packaging secure enough that it won't arrive damaged?","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"row_content":"<p>Our lights are all delivered in special packaging, which is packed with security measures to ensure the light arrives undamaged. We have perfected the necessary level of security after selling more than 100,000 lights!<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_row_U6qaaw","collapsible_row_LQUPAP","collapsible_row_XdcgxH","collapsible_row_NtqQXx","collapsible_row_tq4B9M","collapsible_row_gdGJHz","collapsible_row_dMYAzm"],"settings":{"display_id":false,"visibility":"always-display","c